combine-xmgrace.py    - combine two xmgrace-format files
scraper.py            - general web scraper
average.py            - quick averaging of columnar datafile
extract-bib.py        - extract and collate bibtex records
planetary_sys_trj.py  - make trajectories of solar system
oscillator.py         - simulate probability distn of harmonic oscillator
